* ''Endurance''<ref name="Worsley" />, 1931.
* ''Shackleton's boat journey''<ref name="Worsley" />, 1933. {{ISBN|1-84158-063-5}}
* ''First voyage in a square-rigged ship''<ref name="Worsley" />, 1938.

